WEBVTT

28:36.316 --> 28:37.649
-Is it, really?
-It is.

28:38.358 --> 28:39.358
Be positive.

28:39.358 --> 28:40.566
Mom, why don't you learn
to make this at home?

28:40.608 --> 28:42.066
I could easily make all this.

28:42.066 --> 28:43.149
-Oh sure, Anu.
-Yeah, right!

28:43.149 --> 28:44.691
You wouldn't know.
You're never home.
